window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The Netherworld.</b></p> <p>It is a hellish landscape inhabited only by Demons: creatures born from the dark abyss. But it is also the home of Salvos, and she is finally back. It is no different than she remembered it. A terrible place where only the strongest survive.</p> <p>Can she navigate through Revelation and find her first companion? Or will she get lost in the secrets her father has been hiding?</p>"; 
